(485, 'IIPT M-L-N MND 230020', 'Indosat', 'Nusanet Manado', 'INP 200 Mbps', 'SR#01235336', 'Link Down', '2026-01-21 21:34:00', '2026-01-22 00:20:00', 'Reason For Outage :\r\n1. Submarine Jayabaya cable problem impact transmission problem segment Tanjung Pakis >< Karang Ampel\r\n2. Submarine Jakasusi cable problem impact transmission problem segment Banyuurip >< Takesung\r\n3. Power problem at Site Nangatayap due to MCB KWH PLN 2 phase trip\r\n4. FO cut segment Panempat >< Simpang Tiga Tayan at KM 6.7 from Panempat due to burning activity by reisdents\r\n5. FO cut segment Cepu >< Blora at KM 12 from Cepu due to PLN activity\r\n6. Power problem at Site Bekuak due to PLN off\r\n\r\nAction Taken :\r\n1. Normalize MCB for Site Nangatayap\r\n2. Splicing FO segment Panempat >< Simpang Tiga Tayan\r\n3. Splicing FO segment Cepu >< Blora\r\n4. Power back to normal at Bakuak\r\n5. Reengineering traffic', '2026-01-27 02:08:49', 'nusa-2101265A6', NULL, NULL),
